{"tid":2244630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[告急]奧巴馬見拜登選情嚴峻出山，到搖擺州份造勢","createTime":"2020-10-15T15:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T09:39:16.000Z","uid":123264,"like":120,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"f83f67dedd0e4215db26f919d378453a1f83e0c5","tid":2244630,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/521105-obama-to-stump-for-biden-in-final-campaign-stretch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fcampaign%2F521105-obama-to-stump-for-biden-in-final-campaign-stretch&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=241c6263\" target=\"_blank\">https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/521105-obama-to-stump-for-biden-in-final-campaign-stretch</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFormer President Obama will hit the campaign trail for Democratic nominee Joe Biden in the closing two weeks of the presidential race and is expected to visit key battleground states, sources confirm to The Hill.<br />\n<br />\nDemocrats familiar with the plans say discussions have centered around sending Obama to states like <span class=\"red\">Florida, Pennsylvania, Michigan and Wisconsin</span> &mdash; states the former president and Biden, his vice president, carried in 2008 and 2012.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於現形了<br />\n由一開始biden就係奧巴馬個扯線公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話唔係佢係初選整死bernie sanders 我都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0242d039a08cf235d6995c42db83b73ceb836f50","tid":2244630,"uid":123264,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"呢下好<br />\n拜登唔駛再落場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訓係度都嬴"},{"pid":"19fc0532ac601012ec8f4ae02218f437aa680e6e","tid":2244630,"uid":1